e%20today%20is%20a%20system%20that%20has%20generated%20the%20most%20wealth%20in%20the%20wealthiest%20country%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%20where%20one%20in%20four%20of%20our%20neighbors%20are%20living%20in%20poverty.%20That's%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMamdani%20said%20he%20would%20be%20fighting%20for%20his%20neighbors%20in%20Queens%20who%20own%20small%20businesses%2C%20like%20toy%20stores%20and%20dry%20cleaners%2C%20and%20those%20who%20work%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20right%20now%2C%20all%20of%20them%20are%20being%20pushed%20out%20of%20this%20city%20by%20corporate%20greed%2C%20by%20private%20equity%2C%20and%20by%20a%20politics%20that%20refuses%20to%20fight%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMamdani%20shocked%20New%20York%20City%20this%20summer%20when%20he%20led%20the%20Democratic%20primary%20over%20establishment%20candidate%20former%20Gov.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-mamdani-cuomo-divide-nyc-mayoral-race-change-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Cuomo%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20declared%20the%20winner%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20democratic%20socialist's%20platform%20is%20of%20concern%20to%20some%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20particularly%20his%20aim%20to%20add%20a%202%25%20income%20tax%20to%20those%20making%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20and%20his%20plan%20to%20raise%20corporate%20taxes%20to%2011.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMamdani%20said%20the%20tax%20hikes%20%E2%80%94%20an%20idea%20that%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20said%20she%20would%20be%20resistant%20to%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20used%20to%20fund%20city%20resources%2C%20including%20public%20transportation%20and%20universal%20childcare.%20He%20added%20that%20if%20he%20could%20find%20the%20money%20for%20his%20proposals%20elsewhere%2C%20he'd%20drop%20the%20tax%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20loss%20in%20the%20primary%2C%20Cuomo%20is%20still%20in%20the%20race%20as