e%20company%20ExportNow%2C%20said%20livestream%20commerce%20took%20off%20in%20China%20in%202018%2C%20after%20Alibaba's%20founder%2C%20Jack%20Ma%2C%20challenged%20beauty%20influencer%20Austin%20Li%20to%20sell%20more%20lipsticks%20than%20him%20on%20Alibaba's%20e-commerce%20platform%2C%20Taobao%20Live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20earned%20the%20title%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-li-jiaqi-chinas-lipstick-king-online-shopping-taobao-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina's%20%26quot%3BLipstick%20King%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20sold%2015%2C000%20lipsticks%20in%20five%20minutes%2C%20beating%20Ma's%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Li%20has%20amassed%20a%20following%20of%2035%20million%20on%20Douyin%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eparent%20company%20ByteDance's%20local%20version%20of%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20daily%20streams%20on%20Taobao%20feel%20like%20sensory%20overloads%2C%20with%20an%20endless%20array%20of%20banners%20and%20colorful%20pop-ups.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20most%20famous%20streams%2C%20he%20tested%20380%20lipsticks%20over%20a%20seven-hour%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELive%20shows%20like%20Li's%20are%20%26quot%3Bpart%20shopping%2C%20part%20variety%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jacob%20Cooke%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Beijing-based%20e-commerce%20consulting%20firm%20WPIC%20Marketing%20%2B%20Technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLive%20shows%20blend%20entertainment%2C%20discovery%2C%20and%20transaction%20in%20real%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooke%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20format%20creates%20a%20shared%20social%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20millions%20watching%2C%20commenting%2C%20asking%20questions%20%E2%80%94%20that%20static%20listings%20can't%20replicate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooke%20added%20that%20livestreaming%20in%20China%20got%20a%20leg%20up%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20livestreams%20%26quot%3Bbecame%20a%20way%20to%20replicate%20the%20social%20experience%20of%20shopping%20at%20a%20ma