rset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68edf8d05dbc4fd10daac8f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223027%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rise%20in%20popularity%20of%20collectibles%20is%20giving%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20livestreaming%20industry.%3Cp%3EFREDERIC%20J.%20BROWN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collectibles%20boom%20is%20also%20driving%20the%20livestreaming%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollectibles%20of%20all%20sorts%20%E2%80%94%20board%20games%2C%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20trading%20cards%2C%20blind%20box%20toys%20like%20Labubu%20%E2%80%94%20are%20flying%20off%20the%20shelves%2C%20sought%20after%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkidults-dominate-toy-industry-thanks-to-social-media-pandemic-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econsumer%20group%20called%20%26quot%3Bkidults%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20livestreaming%20is%20the%20collectible%20sellers'%20mechanism%20of%20choice.%20They%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoften%20film%20product%20unboxings%20and%20prove%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20collectibles%20in%20real%20time%20in%20front%20of%20a%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20tuned%20into%20a%20Utah-based%20livestream%20of%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20trading%20cards%20on%20eBay%20Live.%20The%20stream%2C%20which%20had%20about%2050%20viewers%2C%20showed%20a%20seller%20running%20through%20a%20deck%20of%20more%20than%2050%20cards%2C%20briefly%20describing%20each%20one%20over%20energetic%2C%20high-BPM%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHagglers%20bargained%20over%20the%20prices.%20When%20the%20seller%20ripped%20open%20the%20plastic%20covering%20from%20a%20new%20card%20deck%2C%20viewers%20flooded%20the%20screen%20with%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Iannone%2C%20eBay's%20CEO%2C%20said%20in%20a%20September%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BOpening%20Bid%26quot%3B%20that%20eBay%20is%20confident%20about%20the%20future%20of%20livestreaming%20because%20collectibles%20are%20a%20%2410%20billion%20business%20for%20the%20company%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BeBay%20Live%20is%20still%20a%20nascent%20product%2C%20but%20one%20we%20think%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%2C%26quot%3B%20Iannone%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7ae5371-56d8-4d68-a96e-b82b96389eb3%5C%22%3EWhy%20livestreamers%20are%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20viable%20career%20path%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20livestreamers%2C%20the%20career%20path%20offers%20flexible%20working%20hours%2C%20remote%20work%2C%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20make%20money%20from%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaleb%20Wessels%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20beauty%20livestreamer%20from%20Vancouver%2C%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20makeup%20artist%20in%20a%20chain%20drug%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20he%20couldn't%20put%20makeup%20on%20people%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20picked%20by%20Amazon%20to%20be%20a%20creator%20on%20Amazon%20Live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20easy%20to%20get%20started%20%E2%80%94%20he%20already%20had%20ring%20lights%20and%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20can%20jump%20in.%20You%20can%20do%20it%20with%20your%20iPhone%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20does%20not%20have%20a%20fixed%20livestreaming%20schedule%20and%20starts%20streaming%20when%20he%20feels%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20allowed%20him%20to%20keep%20sharing%20makeup%20tips%20and%20swatch%20products%20for%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20loves%20interacting%20with%20people%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20ask%20him%20personal%20questions%20unrelated%20to%20products%20and%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20of%20his%20Amazon%20Live%20livestreams%20in%20October%2C%20Wessels%20answered%20questions%20from%20viewers%20about%20Amazon%20Prime%20Day%20deals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20friendly%20regulars%20who%20asked%20him%20about%20his%20coming%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%2C%20the%20electronics%20livestreamer%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20said%20his%20streams%20are%20%26quot%3Bquite%20relaxed%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20usually%20gets%20asked%20about%20his%20filming%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20both%20Martin%20and%20Wessels%2C%20the%20commissions%20they%20receive%20from%20their%20livestreams%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWessels%20said%20that%20apart%20from%20his%20livestreams%2C%20he%20also%20does%20a%20part-time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-jobs-data-annotators-labelers-outlier-scale-meta-xai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20training%20gig%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20supplement%20his%20income.%20The%20number%20of%20livestreamers%20on%20Amazon%20Live%20has%20increased%20since%20he%20joined%20in%202020%2C%20which%20he%20says%20diluted%20his%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20more%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20livestream%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it's%20spread%20the%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20Wessels%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20went%20from%20sometimes%20hitting%20a%20hundred%20thousand%20viewers%2C%20to%20now%2C%20numbers%20that%20are%20much%20lower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20said%20that%20while%20he%20occasionally%20generates%20livestream%20sales%2C%20he%20focuses%20more%20on%20creating%20content%20for%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%2C%20where%20viewers%20can%20watch%20it%20at%20their%20own%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20hardly%20pays%20me%20anything%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20pay%20my%20bills%20and%20feed%20my%20cats%2C%20that's%20enough%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said%20of%20his%20livestreaming%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-livestreaming-sleepless-selling-machine-us-catching-up-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760659681000%2